==By regions== There are 239,497 registered mosques in Indonesia (2012).<ref name="jumlah masjid">{{cite news |title=Pertumbuhan Masjid di Indonesia Rendah |author=Fenny Melisa|url=http://www.republika.co.id/berita/dunia-islam/islam-nusantara/12/06/03/m51lw4-pertumbuhan-masjid-di-indonesia-rendah |newspaper=Republika |date=June 3, 2012 |accessdate=December 31, 2012}}</ref> To be included in this list, the mosque has to be a landmark of particular region, and most importantly, historically notable. Mosques in bold have been listed in the table above.
